Package fitness

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
fitness.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Fitness class provides all the instances of different classes present. There are three available classes each day and they have their own set times and instructors
Author:
Tanvi Thigle, Leah Ranavat
